quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  56,70,"Haddaan doonno, Waxaan ka dhigeynaa jaan dhanaan oo milix ah (aan la dhami karin), ee maad ku shukridaan (Alle)?"
  56,71,"Ma u fiirsateen dabka aad madagta ka shiddaan."
  56,72,"Ma idinkaa kuwa u soo saara geedaha, mise Annaga (Alle ah) weeye soo saarayaasha?"
  67,10,"Waxay odhan: Haddaan wax maqli laheyn ama garowsan laheyn, kama aanu mid ahaaneyn ehlu Naarka."
  67,11,"Marka waxay qiran denbigooda, ee ha fogaadeen{2} qolada Naarta Hureysa.",footnotes:1:[. Iyagoo laga fogeeyey wax khayr ah oo dhan ama wax Naxariis Ilaahay ah.],footnotes:2:[]
  67,12,"Kuwa ka baqa Rabbigood sir (iyo saaqba) waxay leeyihiin Denbi Dhaaf iyo Ajar Weyn (Janno)."
  68,4,"Waxaa kuu sugnaaday (Nabiyow) dabeecad wanaagsan oo sare."
  68,5,"Marka waad arki, iyaguna (sidoo kale) way arki,"
  68,6,"Kiinna fidmeysan (ama la cadaabo)."
  69,1,"Xaqiiqda dhabta ah ee sugan35>1!",footnotes:1:[. Al-Xaaqqah: Xaqiiqda dhabta ah,waa magac kale oo loo yaqaan Qiyaamaha.],footnotes:2:[]
  69,2,"Waa maxay xaqiiqda dhabta ahi?!"
  69,3,"Maxaad ka og tahay waxay tahay xaqiiqdaa dhabta ahi ee sugan?!"
